<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n03134i"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n03" href="#n03134i">N03 (VI.B.3)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n03all.htm#n03134i"> 134(i)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> in the field</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[from a letter of Mrs PC&apos;s son]</font>: Your sweet letter has just arrived. You don&apos;t know how it cheers one up to get letters from those one loves. / I am sending you my &lsquo;Cross&apos; registered. I do hope it doesn&apos;t get lost. There is no opportunity of wearing it out here <mark>in the field,</mark> and I wear the bit of ribbon on my left breast. <small> Mrs Patrick Campbell, <a name="PCML" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#PCML"><cite title="source">My Life and Some Letters</cite></a> (1922) 394</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
